---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Several Million for Postal Checkout Experience Platform parcelLab - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab completes Series B financing round led by Capnamic Ventures to fuel technology advancement and European expansion."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Several Million for Postal Checkout Experience Platform parcelLab</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2019-11-17">November 17, 2019</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Munich-based parcelLab, a specialist in post-purchase checkout communication, successfully completed its Series B financing round in October 2019. Capnamic Ventures led the investment, joined by existing backers including coparion.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The company plans to deploy the capital toward technology advancement and team expansion across Germany, the UK, and France, while entering new markets.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Customer Loyalty in E-Commerce</h2>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Investor Perspective</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Rising acquisition costs mean customer loyalty matters greatly in retail."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Christian Siegele, Capnamic Ventures</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab operates with approximately 50 employees across Munich, London, and Paris, serving over 350 retailers including IKEA, Lidl, MediaMarktSaturn, and Fressnapf.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">European Growth Strategy</h2>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Investor Perspective</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"parcelLab's solution is technically mature, easily implemented, and delivers impressive metrics."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Christian Schulte, coparion</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Market Opportunity</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Co-founder Anton Eder explained that retailers have optimized pre-purchase experiences extensively, but significant potential remains in post-purchase engagement. Improved shipping communications help retain customers and generate incremental sales through strategic messaging at moments when customer attention is at its peak.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Company Background</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Founded in 2014 by Tobias Buxhoidt, Anton Eder, and Julian Krenge, parcelLab provides white-label solutions delivering real-time delivery monitoring and personalized notifications across email, SMS, and social channels. The platform enables customer journey management and upselling opportunities across 38 countries in 25 languages.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          This funding milestone marks an important step in parcelLab's mission to transform the post-purchase experience for retailers across Europe and beyond. With strong investor backing and a growing customer base, the company is well-positioned to lead the evolution of post-checkout communication.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
